1
00:00:38,500 --> 00:00:40,930
1462年
The year, 1462.

2
00:00:41,800 --> 00:00:44,170
康斯坦丁堡陷落
Constantinople had fallen.

3
00:00:45,010 --> 00:00:48,740
信奉回教的土耳其人大军横扫欧洲
Moslem Turks swept into Europe with a vast, superior force...

4
00:00:49,010 --> 00:00:53,000
痛击罗马尼亚威胁整个基督教世界
striking at Romania, threatening all of Christendom.

5
00:00:53,180 --> 00:00:57,720
川索凡尼亚有一名圣龙会武士
From Transylvania arose a Romanian knight of the Sacred Order of the Dragon,

6
00:00:58,020 --> 00:01:00,420
名叫德古拉
known as Dracula.

7
00:01:16,370 --> 00:01:18,640
战役前夕
On the eve of the battle...

8
00:01:18,770 --> 00:01:24,440
他挚爱的新娘伊丽莎白
his bride Elisabeta whom he prized above all things on Earth...

9
00:01:24,780 --> 00:01:28,980
知道他将与强敌对阵
knew that he must face an insurmountable force...

10
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:32,650
可能一去不返
from which he might never return.

11
00:02:30,580 --> 00:02:32,440
(赞美主)

12
00:02:32,510 --> 00:02:34,450
(我已获胜)

13
00:02:44,130 --> 00:02:46,120
伊丽莎白
Elisabeta.

14
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:52,460
诡诈的土耳其军射箭入城
The vengeful Turks shot an arrow into the castle...

15
00:02:52,970 --> 00:02:56,060
散布德古拉阵亡的谣言
carrying false news of Dracula's death.

16
00:02:56,410 --> 00:02:59,070
伊丽莎白信以为真
Elisabeta, believing him dead...

17
00:02:59,310 --> 00:03:01,970
投河自尽
flung herself into the river.

18
00:03:40,850 --> 00:03:42,840
我的王子死了
My prince is dead.

19
00:03:43,450 --> 00:03:45,580
没有他一切都毫无意义
All is lost without him.

20
00:03:46,250 --> 00:03:48,590
但愿能在天上重逢
May God unite us in heaven.

21
00:04:03,070 --> 00:04:05,130
(她是自尽死的)

22
00:04:05,610 --> 00:04:08,080
(她的灵魂不能升天堂)

23
00:04:09,210 --> 00:04:10,270
(要受天谴)

24
00:04:11,410 --> 00:04:13,280
(这是神的律令)

25
00:04:22,490 --> 00:04:25,950
(这就是我捍卫教会的报偿吗?)

26
00:04:26,030 --> 00:04:27,020
(放肆)

27
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:30,830
(我唾弃上帝)

28
00:04:31,700 --> 00:04:35,360
(我将死后复生)

29
00:04:35,700 --> 00:04:40,110
(用尽邪恶力量为她复仇)

30
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,930
(血是生命泉源)

31
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:05,860
(我将饮血维生)

32
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:42,160
吸血鬼惊情四百年

33
00:05:50,180 --> 00:05:52,910
伦敦,1897年

34
00:05:52,980 --> 00:05:56,970
四个世纪后

35
00:05:57,520 --> 00:06:01,390
(卡费斯区精神病院)

36
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:05,250
我都照你的吩咐做了,主人
I've done everything that you asked, master.

37
00:06:06,730 --> 00:06:10,060
一切准备就绪
All the preparations are in order.

38
00:06:10,130 --> 00:06:11,830
万事俱全
Everything.

39
00:06:11,930 --> 00:06:14,400
我等待你的命令
I await your command.

40
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:16,390
因为
For I know...

41
00:06:17,610 --> 00:06:20,270
当你论功行赏时
that when the rewards are given...

42
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:24,680
你的慷慨会使我受益无穷
I will be one of those who benefits from your generosity.

43
00:06:30,020 --> 00:06:31,350
谢谢
Thank you.

44
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:36,120
伦费发狂了
Gone mad. Renfield is deranged.

45
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:40,020
心智丧失
He's lost his greedy mind, poor chap.

46
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:45,090
替个外国人德古拉伯爵理财
I want you to take over for his foreign client this rather eccentric Count Dracula.

47
00:06:45,100 --> 00:06:47,430
他要在伦敦近郊买房产
- He's buying up property around London. - Of course, sir.

48
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:51,370
我会转告伯爵,谢谢你的委派
I'll attend to the count. Thank you for your confidence.

49
00:06:51,540 --> 00:06:54,440
这是你的大好良机,哈克
This is a great opportunity for you, Harker.

50
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:57,700
但你必须立刻前往川索凡尼亚
But you'll have to leave for Transylvania immediately.

51
00:06:58,180 --> 00:07:01,580
终生难遇的机会
Opportunities such as this come but once in a lifetime.

52
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,680
那当然
Yes, of course, sir.

53
00:07:04,020 --> 00:07:08,510
伦费先生在川索凡尼亚怎么了
If I may inquire...what, in fact, happened to Mr. Renfield in Transylvania?

54
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:11,520
没什么
Nothing. Nothing.

55
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,750
私人问题
Personal problems.

56
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:19,100
完成这些交易你在公司的前途无量
Close these transactions...and your future with this firm is assured.

57
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:22,190
是,我会全力以赴
Yes, sir. I will give it my full attention.

58
00:07:26,170 --> 00:07:28,440
我们等了那么久
We've waited this long, haven't we?

59
00:07:29,010 --> 00:07:31,100
我一回来就结婚
We can be married when I return.

60
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:34,500
好吧
Of course.

61
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,520
我会写信的
I'll write.

62
00:07:37,850 --> 00:07:39,180
强纳生
Jonathan.

63
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,290
强纳生,我爱你
Jonathan, I love you.

64
00:07:46,460 --> 00:07:48,020
我爱你,米娜
I love you, Mina.

65
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:21,060
5月25日,布达佩斯
25th May, Budapest.

66
00:08:21,230 --> 00:08:23,560
今晨离开布达佩斯
Left Budapest early this morning.

67
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,320
依我看...
The impression I had was that we were leaving the west...

68
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:29,530
我们是往东欧前进(强纳生哈克之日记)
and entering the east.

69
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:33,010
这一带是罗马尼亚最东部
The district I am to enter is in the extreme east of the country...

70
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:37,710
摩达维亚、布卡维纳及川索凡尼亚
just on the borders of three states...Transylvania, Moldavia and Bukovina...

71
00:08:37,850 --> 00:08:39,910
喀尔巴阡山交界处
in the midst of the Carpathian Mountains...

72
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:43,410
欧洲最荒凉无名的一区
one of the wildest and least known portions of Europe.

73
00:08:46,590 --> 00:08:48,180
朋友
"My friend...

74
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:51,750
欢迎到喀尔巴阡山
welcome to the Carpathians.

75
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:55,020
久候大驾多时
I am anxiously expecting you.

76
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,430
我的马车
At the Borgo Pass...

77
00:08:57,700 --> 00:09:00,930
将在波戈隘口等你
my carriage will await you and bring you to me.

78
00:09:01,770 --> 00:09:05,710
深信你一路顺畅
I trust yourjourney from London has been a happy one...

79
00:09:06,540 --> 00:09:09,200
并希望你在我国
and that you will enjoy your stay...

80
00:09:09,380 --> 00:09:11,870
身心愉快
in my beautiful land.

81
00:09:12,610 --> 00:09:14,100
你的朋友敬上
Your friend,

82
00:09:16,020 --> 00:09:17,350
德
D."

83
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:27,450
5月25日,日记
Diary, 25th May.

84
00:09:28,130 --> 00:09:31,390
亲爱的强纳生离去近一周(米娜墨瑞之日记)
My Jonathan has been gone almost a week.

85
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:35,260
我虽因不能立刻成婚感到失望
And although I was disappointed we could not marry before his departure...

86
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:38,730
仍为他出使重要任务而高兴
I am happy that he got sent on this important assignment.

87
00:09:38,910 --> 00:09:41,400
我渴望他的音讯
I am longing to hear all the news.

88
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:44,680
到外国一定很有趣
It must be so nice to see strange countries.

89
00:09:45,810 --> 00:09:51,210
不知我们能否一同出国游览
I wonder if we... I mean Jonathan and l...shall ever see them together.

90
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:07,970
我们来早了,还没人来
We're early, driver. No one is here.

91
00:10:09,970 --> 00:10:12,170
(死人才走的快)

92
00:11:27,820 --> 00:11:30,410
城堡远不远?
I say, is the castle far?

93
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:51,900
欢迎光临寒舍
Welcome to my home.

94
00:12:53,070 --> 00:12:55,500
轻松自在地进来
Enter freely of your own will...

95
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:58,330
将你的欢乐留下
and leave some of the happiness you bring.

96
00:12:58,910 --> 00:13:00,340
德古拉伯爵
Count Dracula?

97
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:02,440
在下就是
I am...

98
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:04,500
德古拉
Dracula.

99
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:08,240
寒舍蓬壁生辉了,哈克先生
And I bid you welcome, Mr. Harker, to my house.

100
00:13:11,690 --> 00:13:12,850
请进
Come in.

101
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:32,040
请恕我
You will, I trust, excuse me that I...

102
00:13:32,710 --> 00:13:34,870
不能奉陪
do not join you.

103
00:13:37,610 --> 00:13:40,450
我已经吃过了
But I have already dined.

104
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:43,780
而且我从不喝
And I never drink...

105
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:47,780
葡萄酒
wine.

106
00:13:53,730 --> 00:13:57,060
你的祖先? 五官很像
An ancestor? I see a resemblance.

107
00:13:59,570 --> 00:14:02,040
德古拉的徽记
The Order of the Dracul.

108
00:14:03,970 --> 00:14:05,400
是条龙
The Dragon.

109
00:14:06,740 --> 00:14:08,640
古代有个社
An ancient society...

110
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,910
我的祖先宣誓入会
pledging my forefathers...

111
00:14:13,250 --> 00:14:17,150
保护教会抵御外侮
to defend their church against all enemies of Christ.

112
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:24,090
结果却和教会
That relationship was not entirely...

113
00:14:25,690 --> 00:14:26,680
闹僵
successful.

114
00:14:27,830 --> 00:14:29,630
是吗?
Oh, yes.

115
00:14:33,900 --> 00:14:36,370
这不是开玩笑的事
It is no laughing matter.

116
00:14:39,810 --> 00:14:42,470
我们德古家值得骄傲
We Draculs have a right to be proud.

117
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:46,310
不论阿提拉大帝如何残暴
What devil or witch was ever so great as Attila...

118
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:49,310
我也流着相同的血液
whose blood flows in these veins?

119
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:55,880
血！
Blood...

120
00:15:01,060 --> 00:15:05,060
这年头成宝了
is too precious a thing in these times.

121
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:13,000
杀伐的年代已过去
The warlike days are over.

122
00:15:14,910 --> 00:15:17,740
我家族的光荣战迹
The victories of my great race...

123
00:15:19,180 --> 00:15:21,840
只成为故事
are but a tale to be told.

124
00:15:25,190 --> 00:15:28,590
我是最后一名子嗣
I am the last of my kind.

125
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:34,430
恕我无知,伯爵
I have offended you with my ignorance, Count.

126
00:15:35,700 --> 00:15:37,030
原谅我
Forgive me.

127
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:55,580
我渴望在伦敦拥挤的街道行走
I do so long to go through the crowded streets...of your mighty London...

128
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:59,620
混在匆忙的人群中
to be in the midst of the whirl and the rush of humanity...

129
00:16:00,620 --> 00:16:02,950
分享它的生命力
to share its life...

130
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:04,460
它的改变
its changes,

131
00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:06,060
及死亡
its death.

132
00:16:06,230 --> 00:16:09,060
完成了 伯爵
There. You, Count, are...

133
00:16:12,230 --> 00:16:14,630
你是卡费教堂的所有人
are the owner of Carfax Abbey at Purfleet.

134
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:16,130
恭喜
Congratulations.

135
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:21,540
贵公司对你赞许有加
Your firm writes most highly...of your talents.

136
00:16:21,740 --> 00:16:24,140
他们说你的品味
They say you are a man of good...

137
00:16:25,580 --> 00:16:26,910
很高
taste.

138
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,570
还说你能力不输给
And that you are a worthy substitute...

139
00:16:31,750 --> 00:16:33,910
前任...
to your predecessor,

140
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:36,480
伦费先生
Mr. Renfield.

141
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:38,490
你可以相信我
You may rely on me, Count.

142
00:16:39,430 --> 00:16:40,990
恕我好奇
Forgive my curiosity, but why ten houses...

143
00:16:41,230 --> 00:16:44,560
为何十所房子都买在伦敦附近
in such precise locations around London?

144
00:16:45,300 --> 00:16:47,130
炒地皮?
Is it to raise the market value?

145
00:16:50,370 --> 00:16:52,700
你相信宿命吗
Do you believe in destiny?

146
00:16:55,880 --> 00:16:58,540
时间都可因...
That even the powers of time...

147
00:16:59,510 --> 00:17:00,570
某一...
can be altered for

148
00:17:01,220 --> 00:17:04,150
目的而改变?
a single purpose?

149
00:17:13,230 --> 00:17:19,070
找到真爱的人才是...
The luckiest man who walks on this Earth...is the one who finds...

150
00:17:19,070 --> 00:17:20,730
最幸运的人
true love.

151
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:23,490
你找到米娜了
You found Mina.

152
00:17:24,340 --> 00:17:26,330
我以为丢了呢
I thought she was lost.

153
00:17:26,910 --> 00:17:29,340
我回去后就结婚
We're to be married as soon as I return.

154
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:32,010
你结婚了吗 伯爵?
Are you married, Count?

155
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:34,670
先生
Sir...

156
00:17:35,020 --> 00:17:36,280
你结婚了吗?
are you married?

157
00:17:38,190 --> 00:17:40,180
结过一次
I was married once.

158
00:17:41,260 --> 00:17:43,420
多年以前
Ages ago, it seems.

159
00:17:44,760 --> 00:17:46,090
她死了
She died.

160
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:50,250
真令人难过
I'm very sorry.

161
00:17:50,700 --> 00:17:52,530
是她命好
She was fortunate.

162
00:17:55,270 --> 00:17:58,530
我一生凄凉
My life, at its best, is misery.

163
00:18:03,710 --> 00:18:06,370
她一定会是个贤妻
She will no doubt make a devoted wife.

164
00:18:08,050 --> 00:18:10,610
而你是个忠实的丈夫
And you a faithful husband.

165
00:18:13,990 --> 00:18:14,980
来
Come.

166
00:18:15,820 --> 00:18:18,490
写信给你公司
Write now, my friend, to your firm...

167
00:18:19,330 --> 00:18:23,060
与心爱的人,说你要...
and to any loved ones, and say that it shall please you...

168
00:18:23,530 --> 00:18:27,560
陪我住一个月
to stay with me...until a month from now.

169
00:18:29,140 --> 00:18:30,500
一个月?
A month?

170
00:18:32,340 --> 00:18:33,930
你要我待那么久?
Do you wish me to stay so long?

171
00:18:36,840 --> 00:18:39,180
不可以拒绝
I will take no refusal.

172
00:18:52,130 --> 00:18:54,790
1897年5月3O日,日记
Diary, 30th of May, 1897.

173
00:18:55,860 --> 00:18:59,320
强纳生不愿我在他出差时与露西同住
I know that Jonathan does not want me to stay here with Lucy while he is away.

174
00:19:00,470 --> 00:19:04,630
他怕我习惯威斯丁家的富贵后
He thinks that if I become accustomed to the wealth of the Westenra family...

175
00:19:04,970 --> 00:19:08,810
便不肯当法律事务所职员的妻子
I will not be content as the wife of a mere clerk in a law firm.

176
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:11,880
但我和露西自幼是好友
But Lucy and I have been friends since we were children...

177
00:19:12,050 --> 00:19:15,380
她不在乎我只是个教师
and she has never minded that I am only a schoolmistress.

178
00:19:24,390 --> 00:19:26,330
好恶心
How disgustingly awful.

179
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:30,520
米娜
Mina!

180
00:19:30,830 --> 00:19:31,960
(一千零一夜)

181
00:19:32,330 --> 00:19:33,660
米娜
Mina!

182
00:19:36,600 --> 00:19:39,660
米娜,你老在工作
Oh, Mina, you're always working.

183
00:19:40,910 --> 00:19:45,740
你那有野心的强纳生逼你学打字?
Is your ambitious Jon Harker...forcing you to learn that ridiculous machine?

184
00:19:46,750 --> 00:19:49,180
他也能逼你
When he could be forcing you to perform...

185
00:19:49,250 --> 00:19:53,580
低级热情演出
unspeakable acts of desperate passion on the parlor floor.

186
00:19:53,690 --> 00:19:57,520
露西,你不该这样说我未婚夫
Lucy, really.You shouldn't talk about my fiance in such a way.

187
00:19:58,460 --> 00:20:00,620
婚姻不只是肉体享乐
There's more to marriage than carnal pleasure.

188
00:20:02,060 --> 00:20:05,690
喔 米娜  是哦！
Oh, Mina. So I see.

189
00:20:05,870 --> 00:20:07,860
要多的多
Much, much more.

190
00:20:10,710 --> 00:20:11,690
那是
That's...

191
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:16,870
这是什么?露西
What is it, Lucy?

192
00:20:17,280 --> 00:20:19,710
我看不懂
Because I don't understand it.

193
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:22,640
男女真的...
Can a man and woman really do...

194
00:20:23,380 --> 00:20:24,650
这么做吗?
that?

195
00:20:24,820 --> 00:20:27,250
我昨晚就做过
I did, only last night.

196
00:20:27,320 --> 00:20:28,620
骗人!你没有
Fibber. You did not.

197
00:20:28,690 --> 00:20:30,350
我有
Yes, I did.

198
00:20:31,490 --> 00:20:33,480
在我的梦里
Well, in my dreams.

199
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:36,990
强纳生有这么棒吧?
Jonathan measures up, doesn't he?

200
00:20:37,570 --> 00:20:39,500
你可以告诉我的
You can tell Lucy.

201
00:20:40,500 --> 00:20:42,940
我们只接过吻
We've kissed. That's all.

202
00:20:43,670 --> 00:20:46,160
他觉得娶不起我
He thinks he's too poor to marry me.

203
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:50,680
更糟的是我到你的华宅看你
And it's all the worse now that I'm here visiting you at Hillingham...

204
00:20:50,910 --> 00:20:52,400
我的富有朋友
my rich friend.

205
00:20:53,010 --> 00:20:55,910
却没人向我求过婚
Yes, but not even one marriage proposal.

206
00:20:56,250 --> 00:20:58,580
我快满20了
And here I am, almost 20...

207
00:20:58,750 --> 00:21:00,690
是个老处女了
practically a hag.

208
00:21:07,030 --> 00:21:09,520
昆西摩里斯先生到
Mr. Quincey P. Morris.

209
00:21:11,270 --> 00:21:12,600
你看
Oh, look.

210
00:21:13,270 --> 00:21:14,860
那是什么人
What is that?

211
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:16,430
德州人
A Texan.

212
00:21:17,370 --> 00:21:19,430
昆西摩里斯
Quincey P. Morris.

213
00:21:20,110 --> 00:21:22,440
他好年轻稚气
He's so young and fresh...

214
00:21:22,710 --> 00:21:24,870
像我胯间的野种马
like a wild stallion between my legs.

215
00:21:25,050 --> 00:21:26,880
你真下流
You're positively indecent.

216
00:21:27,050 --> 00:21:29,040
我只是知道男人想要什么
I just know what men desire.

217
00:21:29,620 --> 00:21:30,950
看着
Watch.

218
00:21:31,650 --> 00:21:32,980
昆西达令
Quincey, darling.

219
00:21:33,050 --> 00:21:34,540
露西小姐
Miss Lucy.

220
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:37,220
你像春雨般清新
Why, you're as fresh as the spring rain.

221
00:21:37,390 --> 00:21:38,880
谢谢
Oh, thank you.

222
00:21:40,290 --> 00:21:41,780
昆西
Quincey.

223
00:21:43,100 --> 00:21:45,530
求求你让我摸摸
Please let me touch it.

224
00:21:46,630 --> 00:21:47,620
好...
It's so...

225
00:21:48,470 --> 00:21:49,730
大
big.

226
00:21:52,810 --> 00:21:54,140
小女孩
Little girl.

227
00:21:54,810 --> 00:21:57,240
我亲爱的小女孩
Oh, my dear, sweet little girl.

228
00:21:57,650 --> 00:22:00,580
我握着你的手,你也吻过我
I hold your hand...- and you've kissed me.

229
00:22:01,220 --> 00:22:02,740
杰克
Jack!

230
00:22:03,650 --> 00:22:05,640
爱你深似海
Oceans of love... Oh, Jack, my darling.

231
00:22:06,420 --> 00:22:08,980
我的达令,小宝贝
Poor little baby.

232
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:10,990
小猫咪过来
My kitten, come over here.

233
00:22:11,590 --> 00:22:13,320
来,吻一个就会好了
Come over here and I'll kiss it better.

234
00:22:13,930 --> 00:22:15,760
我可怜的小花
My poor little blossom.

235
00:22:16,100 --> 00:22:19,090
我可怜的小郎中,小医生
My poor little doctor. Brilliant doctor.

236
00:22:19,130 --> 00:22:20,670
嗨 昆西   杰克
- Hello, Quincey. - Jack.

237
00:22:20,670 --> 00:22:22,900
坏熊,我摸摸爪子
What a naughty bear. Let me...

238
00:22:22,970 --> 00:22:25,270
阿瑟荷伍先生到
Arthur Holmwood, Esquire.

239
00:22:25,570 --> 00:22:26,700
阿瑟
Arthur!

240
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:29,430
亲爱的
Oh, my darling.

241
00:22:30,340 --> 00:22:32,780
你气色真好
Oh, you look wonderful.

242
00:22:32,950 --> 00:22:34,440
抱歉弄坏你的帽子
I'm so sorry about your hat.

243
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:36,470
好美 这是我的妖女装
- Charming. - It's my snake dress.

244
00:22:36,550 --> 00:22:38,520
真的吗?
Is it really?

245
00:22:39,020 --> 00:22:41,610
露西纯洁有德
Lucy is a pure and virtuous girl...

246
00:22:41,790 --> 00:22:45,350
但她言语大胆真叫我震惊
but I admit that her free way of speaking shocks me sometimes.

247
00:22:46,130 --> 00:22:51,460
强纳生说贵族都是口无遮拦
Jonathan says it is a defect of the aristocracy...that they say what they please.

248
00:22:51,470 --> 00:22:53,370
但我崇拜露西
The truth is that I admire Lucy,

249
00:22:53,530 --> 00:22:56,300
难怪男人爱她
and I'm not surprised that men flock around her.

250
00:22:56,800 --> 00:22:59,640
我希望我像她一样漂亮迷人
I wish I were as pretty and as adored as she.

251
00:23:17,830 --> 00:23:20,160
他是怎样的人?
What manner of man is this?

252
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:23,220
亚伦费,霍汤公司得力干部
R.M. Renfield, successful solicitor...

253
00:23:23,300 --> 00:23:29,240
法律俱乐部受人尊敬的会员(西渥医生之语音日记)
in the firm of Hawkins and Thompkins...respected member of the Lord Nugent's Windem Club...

254
00:23:29,240 --> 00:23:32,830
从川索凡尼亚出差回来
returns from business abroad in Transylvania...

255
00:23:33,910 --> 00:23:36,900
精神完全崩溃
promptly suffers a complete mental breakdown.

256
00:23:37,340 --> 00:23:40,680
他现在嗜血如命
He's now obsessed with some blood lust.

257
00:23:44,450 --> 00:23:46,110
乔治
George.

258
00:23:48,260 --> 00:23:49,520
在这里等一下
Wait here.

259
00:23:57,430 --> 00:24:02,270
吃开胃菜?西渥先生
Would you care for an hors d'oeuvre, Dr. Seward...

260
00:24:02,270 --> 00:24:03,530
还是点心?
or a canape?

261
00:24:03,700 --> 00:24:05,370
不了,谢谢,伦费先生
No, thank you, Mr. Renfield.

262
00:24:05,540 --> 00:24:07,030
今晚感觉如何?
How are you feeling tonight?

263
00:24:08,210 --> 00:24:10,770
比你好,单相思医生
Far better than you, my lovesick doctor.

264
00:24:11,080 --> 00:24:13,770
你对我的私生活有兴趣
Is my personal life of interest to you?

265
00:24:13,950 --> 00:24:16,440
对,我对所有人都有兴趣
Of course it is. All life interests me.

266
00:24:16,950 --> 00:24:18,380
你的食物,伦费先生
Your diet, Mr. Renfield, is disgusting.

267
00:24:18,620 --> 00:24:19,880
真恶心
Actually,

268
00:24:20,120 --> 00:24:22,880
实际上很营养
they're perfectly nutritious.

269
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:26,390
我所摄取的生命
You see, each life that I ingest...

270
00:24:26,630 --> 00:24:28,790
会带给我生命
gives back life to me.

271
00:24:32,630 --> 00:24:34,620
苍蝇带给你生命?
A fly gives you life?

272
00:24:35,300 --> 00:24:36,630
没错
Certainly.

273
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:41,500
叫我吃一般食物
But you might as well ask a man to eat molecules with a pair of chopsticks...

274
00:24:41,580 --> 00:24:44,310
比用筷子夹分子还难
than to interest me in a lesser carnivore.

275
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:47,970
我要为你发明疯子新分类法
I shall have to invent a new classification of lunatic for you.

276
00:24:49,180 --> 00:24:52,910
蜘蛛你吃吗?蜘蛛吃苍蝇
What about spiders? Spiders eat the flies.

277
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:56,910
是的,蜘蛛吃苍蝇
Yes, spiders eat them.

278
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:58,820
麻雀你吃吗?
What about sparrows?

279
00:24:59,660 --> 00:25:00,990
吃！
Oh, yes.

280
00:25:01,730 --> 00:25:03,090
你刚说麻雀吗?
Did you say sparrows?

281
00:25:03,260 --> 00:25:05,250
体型大点的
Something larger, perhaps?

282
00:25:06,000 --> 00:25:07,330
对
Oh, yes.

283
00:25:08,770 --> 00:25:10,500
小猫
A kitten.

284
00:25:10,940 --> 00:25:12,270
求求你
I beg you.

285
00:25:12,670 --> 00:25:14,270
一只...
A little, sleek... a playful kitten.

286
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:17,010
受教爱玩
Something I can teach. Something I can feed.

287
00:25:17,180 --> 00:25:21,170
可喂食的小猫 小猫而已嘛
No one would refuse me a kitten.

288
00:25:21,450 --> 00:25:23,610
成猫好吗
Wouldn't you prefer a cat?

289
00:25:25,950 --> 00:25:27,280
好
Oh, yes.

290
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:29,010
一只大猫
A big cat.

291
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:31,960
我的救赎全靠它了
- My salvation depends upon it! - Your salvation?

292
00:25:32,090 --> 00:25:33,560
你的救赎?没错
Yes. I need lives.

293
00:25:33,630 --> 00:25:36,960
我需要生物,好献给主人
I need lives for the master.

294
00:25:37,030 --> 00:25:38,330
什么主人
What master?

295
00:25:40,770 --> 00:25:42,930
主人即将抵达
The master will come...

296
00:25:44,370 --> 00:25:47,770
他答应要让我不朽
and he has promised to make me immortal.

297
00:25:47,780 --> 00:25:49,330
用什么方法?
How?

298
00:25:50,910 --> 00:25:52,640
把他拉开！
Get him off!

299
00:25:53,950 --> 00:25:56,040
血便是生命
The blood is the life!

300
00:25:57,450 --> 00:25:59,390
血便是生命
The blood is the life!

301
00:26:01,120 --> 00:26:03,560
5月30日,德古拉城堡
30th May, Castle Dracula.

302
00:26:03,790 --> 00:26:07,730
我发现怪异难言的事
I think strange things which I dare not confess to my own soul.

303
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:09,620
伯爵
The count...

304
00:26:09,800 --> 00:26:13,290
看米娜照片的神情让我害怕
the way he looked at Mina's picture fills me with dread...

305
00:26:13,470 --> 00:26:16,600
我仿佛置身在谜团中
as if I have a part to play in a story that is not known to me.

306
00:26:41,430 --> 00:26:42,760
我没听到你进来
I didn't hear you come in.

307
00:26:46,330 --> 00:26:48,890
小心割到
Take care how you cut yourself.

308
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:52,840
刀子比你想象的危险
It is more dangerous than you think.

309
00:26:59,280 --> 00:27:03,680
人类虚荣造出的 邪恶东西
A foul bauble of man's vanity.

310
00:27:04,280 --> 00:27:05,770
也许你可以
Perhaps you should...

311
00:27:06,690 --> 00:27:08,350
蓄须
grow a beard.

312
00:27:16,460 --> 00:27:18,120
我要你写的信
The letters I requested.

313
00:27:19,370 --> 00:27:21,200
写了吗?
Have you written them?

314
00:27:38,320 --> 00:27:39,310
很好
Good.

315
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:51,830
你若离开这几间房间
Should you leave these rooms...

316
00:27:53,670 --> 00:27:56,070
劝你切勿...
you will not, by any chance...

317
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:59,070
到堡内其他区域过夜
go to sleep in any other part of the castle.

318
00:28:01,070 --> 00:28:03,240
古堡内
It is old...

319
00:28:04,510 --> 00:28:07,170
有许多可怕的回忆
and has many bad memories.

320
00:28:09,520 --> 00:28:10,920
我警告过你了
Be warned.

321
00:28:11,080 --> 00:28:12,680
我充份了解
I'm sure I understand.

322
00:28:21,700 --> 00:28:24,100
不要相信这种
Do not put your faith in

323
00:28:24,260 --> 00:28:25,700
小玩意
such trinkets of deceit.

324
00:28:27,370 --> 00:28:28,700
我们在
We are in

325
00:28:28,870 --> 00:28:30,200
川索凡尼亚
Transylvania.

326
00:28:30,370 --> 00:28:34,270
而...川索凡尼亚不同于英国
Transylvania is not England.

327
00:28:35,440 --> 00:28:38,100
我们的风俗习惯与你们不同
Our ways are not your ways.

328
00:28:38,710 --> 00:28:40,200
你一定会
And to you...

329
00:28:40,980 --> 00:28:44,140
觉得很怪异
there shall be many strange things.

330
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:47,390
我已经看到许多怪事
I've seen many strange things already.

331
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:51,050
狼群追逐我穿过蓝色炼狱
Bloody wolves chasing me through some blue inferno!

332
00:28:56,560 --> 00:28:58,720
你听听
Listen to them.

333
00:29:03,340 --> 00:29:05,830
夜童的哭号
The children of the night.

334
00:29:08,410 --> 00:29:10,840
多美妙的音乐
What sweet music they make.

335
00:29:11,510 --> 00:29:12,500
音乐
Music?

336
00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:14,170
那群野兽?
Those animals?

337
00:29:48,150 --> 00:29:50,580
我照德古拉的意思写了三封信
I did as Dracula instructed. I wrote three letters.

338
00:29:50,750 --> 00:29:55,650
给公司、家人以及心爱的米娜
To the firm, to my family and to my beloved Mina.

339
00:29:56,090 --> 00:29:59,080
我没提及我的恐惧
I said nothing of my fears as he will read them, no doubt.

340
00:30:04,260 --> 00:30:06,760
因为我知道我成了囚犯
I know now that I am a prisoner.

341
00:31:32,390 --> 00:31:33,580
强纳生！
Jonathan.

342
00:31:35,360 --> 00:31:37,690
强纳生,到我身边
Jonathan, come to me.

343
00:31:47,370 --> 00:31:48,700
来
Come.

344
00:32:07,650 --> 00:32:09,210
躺下
Lay down.

345
00:32:10,720 --> 00:32:12,660
躺在我怀里
Lay back into my arms.

346
00:32:22,300 --> 00:32:24,070
躺下
Lay back, Jonathan.

347
00:34:16,250 --> 00:34:17,680
(你们干嘛)

348
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:18,810
(冒牌货)

349
00:34:25,890 --> 00:34:27,620
(不准碰他)

350
00:34:27,690 --> 00:34:29,690
(他是我的)

351
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:32,220
(你从没恋爱过)

352
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:40,030
(有,我能恋爱)

353
00:34:42,180 --> 00:34:46,240
(而且我将再次恋爱)

354
00:34:54,650 --> 00:34:57,380
(那我们今晚没血喝了吗?)

355
00:35:34,260 --> 00:35:36,420
(葳荷米娜墨瑞,希灵汉庄园)

356
00:35:41,530 --> 00:35:44,230
吾爱米娜：一切均安
"Dearest Mina, all is well here.

357
00:35:44,540 --> 00:35:49,370
伯爵要我住一个月教他英国礼俗
The count has insisted I remain for a month...to tutor him in English custom.

358
00:35:49,810 --> 00:35:52,540
别他无语,只有我爱你
I can say no more, except I love you.

359
00:35:53,250 --> 00:35:55,650
忠实至终的强纳生上
Ever faithful, Jonathan."

360
00:35:59,290 --> 00:36:03,020
这些信让我陷入绝境
The letters I have written have undoubtedly sealed my doom.

361
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:08,620
伯爵的吉普赛人
The count's gypsies...

362
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:13,030
英勇战士们  效忠这位贵族,死而无惧
fearless warriors who are loyal to the death to whatever nobleman they serve...

363
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:17,890
他们日夜工作
day and night they toil,

364
00:36:18,170 --> 00:36:23,000
将城堡的土装箱
filling boxes with decrepit earth...from the bowels of the castle.

365
00:36:24,040 --> 00:36:28,540
运到刚购入的伦敦卡费教堂
They are to be delivered to his newly acquired Carfax Abbey in London.

366
00:36:30,650 --> 00:36:33,550
为什么要装土呢?
Why do they fill these boxes with earth?

367
00:36:40,060 --> 00:36:42,390
我爱他!我爱他
I love him! I love him!

368
00:36:43,030 --> 00:36:44,720
米娜
Mina.

369
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:48,160
妙不可言,我决定了
It's so wonderful. I've decided.

370
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:51,000
我爱他,我要嫁他
I love him and I've said yes.

371
00:36:51,170 --> 00:36:53,260
总算!你先别说
Finally. Don't tell me.

372
00:36:53,410 --> 00:36:55,400
带大刀的德州人? 不！
The Texan with the big knife? Oh, no.

373
00:36:55,680 --> 00:36:57,670
我要嫁第三号
To my dear number three.

374
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:59,400
阿瑟荷伍爵爷
Lord Arthur Holmwood.

375
00:36:59,580 --> 00:37:01,740
荷伍勋爵夫妇
Lord and Lady Holmwood.

376
00:37:01,920 --> 00:37:04,680
你做伴娘,答应吧
You are to be my maid of honor. Oh, say yes.

377
00:37:05,290 --> 00:37:08,580
怎么回事?今天是我大喜
Mina, what is it? It's the most exciting day of my life.

378
00:37:10,390 --> 00:37:11,720
你好像漠不关心
You don't seem to care.

379
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:15,620
我只是很担心强纳生
It's just that I'm so terribly worried about Jonathan.

380
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:18,130
来信语气冷淡
This letter I received is so...

381
00:37:18,300 --> 00:37:21,890
很不寻常,根本不像他
It's so cold. It's so unnatural. It's not like him at all.

382
00:37:23,240 --> 00:37:24,790
别担心
Mina, don't worry.

383
00:37:51,460 --> 00:37:53,630
丰饶女神号,船长日志
Captain's log: : The Demeter.

384
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:55,960
1897年6月27日
27thJune, 1897.

385
00:37:58,970 --> 00:38:01,870
我们载了50箱实验用土
We picked up 50 boxes of experimental earth...

386
00:38:02,040 --> 00:38:03,980
前往英国伦敦
bound for London, England.

387
00:38:04,310 --> 00:38:09,340
一场莫名风暴来袭
Set sail at noon into a storm...that seemed to come out of nowhere...

388
00:38:09,450 --> 00:38:11,710
将我们推向汪洋
carrying us out to sea.

389
00:38:33,440 --> 00:38:35,240
(伦敦动物园)

390
00:38:46,850 --> 00:38:48,580
7月3日
Third ofJuly.

391
00:38:48,690 --> 00:38:50,590
第二名船员失踪
Second mate has gone missing.

392
00:38:50,690 --> 00:38:52,350
接近直布罗陀海峡
Nearing Gibraltar.

393
00:38:52,490 --> 00:38:53,930
风暴持续肆虐
Storm continues.

394
00:38:54,090 --> 00:38:55,750
船员非常不安
Crew uneasy.

395
