00:59:01,910 --> 00:59:03,170
我找不出原因
I cannot trace the cause.

592
00:59:03,310 --> 00:59:04,670
失血?怎么会
Blood loss? How?

593
00:59:14,490 --> 00:59:15,820
把门关上
My God, close the doors!

594
00:59:27,330 --> 00:59:28,490
天啊
My God...

595
00:59:28,770 --> 00:59:30,500
她还是个孩子
she's only a child.

596
00:59:32,370 --> 00:59:33,800
是啊
Ja.

597
00:59:35,170 --> 00:59:36,570
老天！
My God.

598
00:59:37,680 --> 00:59:41,910
不得延误立刻输血,脱掉外套
There's no time to lose. There must be a transfusion at once.Take off your coat.

599
00:59:42,780 --> 00:59:45,110
还会绑止血带吧
Remember how to tie a tourniquet?Or have you forgotten?

600
00:59:45,250 --> 00:59:46,580
你精通输血?
You perfected a procedure?

601
00:59:47,020 --> 00:59:51,190
精通?不,我只会蓝斯坦法
Perfected? No. I've only experimented.Landsteiner's method.

602
00:59:53,020 --> 00:59:55,180
只替动物输过,山羊、绵羊啦
Animals, goats, sheeps.

603
00:59:56,760 --> 01:00:00,660
若血清有溶血现象红血球会破裂
If hemolysis occurs in the blood donor serum...her red blood cells will explode.

604
01:00:01,000 --> 01:00:03,090
她就会死,把管子拿好
She will die. Take this tube.

605
01:00:07,200 --> 01:00:09,170
你们在搞什么
What in God's name is going on up here?

606
01:00:09,370 --> 01:00:10,930
这位是梵海辛教授
This is Professor Van Helsing, Art.

607
01:00:11,110 --> 01:00:12,410
他把露西怎么了
What the hell is he doing to Lucy?

608
01:00:12,510 --> 01:00:13,770
救她的命
He's trying to save her life.

609
01:00:13,880 --> 01:00:14,640
老天！
Good God!

610
01:00:14,710 --> 01:00:15,910
你是她的未婚夫
You're the fiance?

611
01:00:15,980 --> 01:00:17,140
请让开
Please.

612
01:00:17,880 --> 01:00:19,110
请！
Please.

613
01:00:20,020 --> 01:00:24,780
外套脱掉,她生命垂危须输血
Take off your coat. This young lady's very ill. She's dying.She wants blood and blood she must have.

614
01:00:25,360 --> 01:00:26,690
外套脱掉！
Take off your coat.

615
01:00:26,890 --> 01:00:28,450
袖子卷起来
Roll up your sleeve, Art.

616
01:00:30,090 --> 01:00:32,220
老天！快！
- Oh, God. - Quickly, quickly.

617
01:00:32,460 --> 01:00:33,790
卷起来
Roll it up!

618
01:00:34,170 --> 01:00:35,960
可能有点痛
This may hurt a little, Art.

619
01:00:47,650 --> 01:00:52,050
请原谅我  她是我的命,最后一滴血都行
Forgive me. My life is hers. I would give my last drop of blood to save her.

620
01:00:52,250 --> 01:00:53,310
最后一滴?
Your last drop?

621
01:00:54,080 --> 01:00:56,310
谢谢,欢迎你
Thank you.You are very welcome here.

622
01:00:56,490 --> 01:00:58,460
我不要那么多
I don't ask as much as that.

623
01:00:58,560 --> 01:00:59,650
目前还不要
Not yet.

624
01:00:59,860 --> 01:01:01,190
握住她的手
Hold her hand.

625
01:01:13,470 --> 01:01:18,040
杰克...她输了两人份的血
Jack, that poor creature has had the blood of two men put into her already.

626
01:01:18,210 --> 01:01:21,800
妈呀!她装不了那么多血
Man alive. Her whole body couldn't hold that much blood.

627
01:01:24,820 --> 01:01:26,180
露西的血去哪呢
What took it out?

628
01:01:26,250 --> 01:01:28,280
问的好,摩里斯先生
That's a good question, Mr. Morris.

629
01:01:33,560 --> 01:01:35,490
喉咙那些痕迹?
Those marks on her throat...

630
01:01:35,730 --> 01:01:40,160
不是疾病或伤痕,而是失血处
no disease, no trituration...I am sure the blood loss occurred there.

631
01:01:40,560 --> 01:01:42,620
血去哪呢?
Oh? Where did the blood go?

632
01:01:43,630 --> 01:01:46,070
你以前是个细心的学生
You were once a careful student, Jack.

633
01:01:46,300 --> 01:01:48,240
用脑呀,血去哪了?告诉我!
Use your brain! Where did the blood go?Tell me!

634
01:01:50,570 --> 01:01:52,970
床铺上有血   没错
- The bed would be covered in blood. - Exactly.

635
01:01:53,310 --> 01:01:57,970
你没观察到不可知的现象
You do not let your eyes see nor your ears hear...that which you cannot account for.

636
01:01:58,150 --> 01:02:02,140
有异物吸她的血后飞走?
Something just went up there, sucked it out of her and flew away?

637
01:02:03,850 --> 01:02:05,410
对 有何不可?
Ja. Why not?

638
01:02:06,520 --> 01:02:09,860
高明,真高明
That's brilliant. That's absolutely brilliant.

639
01:02:10,190 --> 01:02:14,190
请问神医,露西是怎么了?
Will one of you learned doctors... or whatever you are...kindly tell me what is going on with my Lucy?

640
01:02:15,670 --> 01:02:18,100
杰克,你是个科学家
Jack, you are a scientist.

641
01:02:18,540 --> 01:02:22,940
宇宙中可有你不明了的事实?
Do you not think there are things in this universe you cannot understand...and which are true...

642
01:02:23,140 --> 01:02:24,470
像是催眠
mesmerism, hypnotism?

643
01:02:24,610 --> 01:02:26,340
你和夏卡已证实了
You and Charcot have proved hypnotism.

644
01:02:26,540 --> 01:02:29,270
实体与灵体
Materialization, astral bodies.

645
01:02:37,960 --> 01:02:39,290
教授?
Professor?

646
01:02:41,460 --> 01:02:42,690
他去哪了
Where did he go?

647
01:02:45,900 --> 01:02:46,790
看到了吧
You see?

648
01:02:47,900 --> 01:02:50,300
我像是个菜乌
I feel like a blundering novice.

649
01:02:50,570 --> 01:02:53,370
我们对抗的不是疾病
Gentlemen, we're not fighting some disease here.

650
01:02:54,240 --> 01:02:58,540
露西小姐的咬痕是妖魔所致
Those marks on your dear Miss Lucy's neck were made...by something unspeakable out there.

651
01:02:58,540 --> 01:02:59,870
已死又未死
Dead, but not dead.

652
01:03:00,210 --> 01:03:03,110
妖魔追猎我们,原因不明
It stalks us for some dread purpose I do not comprehend.

653
01:03:03,380 --> 01:03:06,140
它吸露西的血维持生命
To live, it feeds on Lucy's precious blood.

654
01:03:06,320 --> 01:03:08,810
是个野兽,怪物
It is a beast, a monster.

655
01:03:27,240 --> 01:03:30,400
我和露西是怎么了
What is happening to Lucy and to me?

656
01:03:30,640 --> 01:03:33,630
年幼时我从不烦躁
When I was younger, my feelings were never troubled.

657
01:03:33,880 --> 01:03:36,070
真希望能恢复往日
I wish I were myself again...

658
01:03:36,250 --> 01:03:39,080
那么敏锐,永可依赖的米娜
the sensible Mina I always depended on.

659
01:03:46,660 --> 01:03:48,250
艾伯森酒
Absinthe...

660
01:03:48,830 --> 01:03:51,660
含春药的成份
is the aphrodisiac of the self.

661
01:03:53,560 --> 01:03:55,260
住在酒里的...
The green fairy...

662
01:03:55,830 --> 01:03:59,570
绿仙子
who lives in the absinthe...

663
01:04:00,970 --> 01:04:02,730
要你的灵魂
wants your soul.

664
01:04:05,580 --> 01:04:06,670
但是
But...

665
01:04:08,350 --> 01:04:10,180
你可以放心
you are safe with me.

666
01:04:26,030 --> 01:04:27,790
王子...
Tell me, Prince...

667
01:04:28,470 --> 01:04:30,590
告诉我你家乡的事
tell me of your home.

668
01:04:33,300 --> 01:04:37,610
全世界最美丽的地方
The most beautiful place...in all creation.

669
01:04:38,440 --> 01:04:42,310
一定是
Yes, it must be.

670
01:04:46,050 --> 01:04:48,380
森林
A land beyond a great,

671
01:04:48,550 --> 01:04:49,950
密布
vast forest...

672
01:04:52,620 --> 01:04:55,620
山峦起伏
surrounded by majestic mountains...

673
01:04:57,290 --> 01:04:59,130
葡萄园
lush vineyards...

674
01:05:01,400 --> 01:05:05,570
遍地无处可比拟的
and flowers of such frailty and beauty...

675
01:05:05,900 --> 01:05:08,340
妖艳花朵
as to be found nowhere else.

676
01:05:18,180 --> 01:05:22,180
你说的好像亲眼看过
You've described my home...as if you had seen it firsthand.

677
01:05:26,590 --> 01:05:28,890
或许受你的声调影响
It's your voice, perhaps.

678
01:05:29,660 --> 01:05:31,590
好熟悉
It's so familiar.

679
01:05:33,900 --> 01:05:35,230
仿佛...
It's like...

680
01:05:36,900 --> 01:05:40,100
梦中无法认出的声音
It's like a voice in a dream I cannot place...

681
01:05:42,770 --> 01:05:44,760
在我孤独时
and it comforts me.

682
01:05:45,610 --> 01:05:47,440
安抚我  在你孤独时
- When I am alone. - When you are alone.

683
01:06:09,970 --> 01:06:12,060
王妃呢?
And what of the princess?

684
01:06:18,880 --> 01:06:20,210
王妃?
Princess?

685
01:06:20,410 --> 01:06:22,740
有王子就有王妃
There is always a princess...

686
01:06:24,650 --> 01:06:27,140
穿着白衣裙
with gowns flowing white.

687
01:06:30,750 --> 01:06:34,320
她的脸
And her face.

688
01:06:34,590 --> 01:06:35,890
天啊
Oh, God...

689
01:06:37,760 --> 01:06:39,230
她的脸
her face...

690
01:06:43,430 --> 01:06:44,700
是条河
is a river.

691
01:06:50,240 --> 01:06:51,900
王妃
The princess...

692
01:06:52,910 --> 01:06:57,310
是条....充满伤痛
she's a river filled with tears of sadness...

693
01:06:58,150 --> 01:07:00,740
心碎泪水的河
and heartbreak.

694
01:07:04,220 --> 01:07:06,160
是有过王妃
There was a princess.

695
01:07:09,830 --> 01:07:11,160
伊丽莎白
Elisabeta.

696
01:07:14,260 --> 01:07:18,430
她是全世界最耀眼的女子
She was the most radiant woman...in all the empires of the world.

697
01:07:26,110 --> 01:07:29,550
谣言拆散了她与王子
Man's deceit took her from her ancient prince.

698
01:07:31,620 --> 01:07:33,110
她投入...
She leapt to her death...

699
01:07:33,720 --> 01:07:36,850
你提到的河而死
into the river that you spoke of.

700
01:07:38,190 --> 01:07:41,550
我的 母语...
In my mother's tongue...

701
01:07:42,560 --> 01:07:47,920
那条河叫
it is called...argesh.

702
01:07:50,000 --> 01:07:51,870
王妃河
River princess.

703
01:09:28,530 --> 01:09:29,760
亲爱的女士
Dear Madam.

704
01:09:29,830 --> 01:09:32,960
你的未婚夫在修道院(阿格莎修女8月12日之信)
Your fiance is safe and in the care...

705
01:09:33,040 --> 01:09:35,440
安然无恙
of the good sisters of the Blessed Sacrament.

706
01:09:37,040 --> 01:09:41,140
哈克先生认为你有生命危险
Mr. Harker believes your life is in extreme danger...

707
01:09:41,340 --> 01:09:44,910
他急切希望你到此
and he desires with all urgency that you join him here...

708
01:09:45,080 --> 01:09:47,920
立刻成婚
so that you may immediately be married.

709
01:09:48,150 --> 01:09:50,380
祝福你
Yours with all blessings,

710
01:09:50,520 --> 01:09:52,350
阿格莎修女上
Sister Agatha.

711
01:09:55,030 --> 01:09:56,820
亲爱的王子
My sweet prince.

712
01:09:57,560 --> 01:09:59,930
绝不能让强纳生知道
Jonathan must never know of us.

713
01:10:07,600 --> 01:10:09,270
露西
Lucy!

714
01:10:09,340 --> 01:10:10,930
我是亚拉汉梵海辛
I'm Abraham Van Helsing.

715
01:10:11,170 --> 01:10:12,510
梵海辛博士
Dr. Van Helsing.

716
01:10:12,680 --> 01:10:15,580
你是米娜小姐,露西的好友?
And you're Madam Mina, dear friend to our Lucy, ja?

717
01:10:16,010 --> 01:10:17,100
她怎样了
How is she, doctor?

718
01:10:17,150 --> 01:10:18,940
仍很虚弱
She's still very weak.

719
01:10:19,250 --> 01:10:23,750
她告诉我你担心你爱的强纳生
She tells me of your beloved Jonathan Harker...and your worry for him.

720
01:10:24,120 --> 01:10:26,780
我为所有的年轻爱侣担心
Well, I, too, worry for all young lovers.

721
01:10:30,960 --> 01:10:32,950
生命中有黑暗
There are darknesses in life, my child...

722
01:10:33,530 --> 01:10:35,460
也有光明
and there are lights.

723
01:10:35,630 --> 01:10:38,290
你便是光明,亲爱的米娜
You are one of the lights, dear Mina...

724
01:10:38,540 --> 01:10:40,730
光明中的光明
the light of all light.

725
01:10:46,210 --> 01:10:47,570
去看你的朋友吧
Go now. See your friend.

726
01:11:04,330 --> 01:11:05,790
米娜
Mina.

727
01:11:09,170 --> 01:11:11,160
你不太一样,米娜
You look different,Mina.

728
01:11:11,940 --> 01:11:14,500
脸上发光
You look positively radiant.

729
01:11:15,110 --> 01:11:16,540
有强纳生的消息
You heard from Jonathan.

730
01:11:16,540 --> 01:11:19,860
是吗?  嗯
- Didn't you? - Yes.

731
01:11:20,510 --> 01:11:22,440
他平安无事,露西
He's safe,Lucy.

732
01:11:22,780 --> 01:11:25,180
在罗马尼亚一家修道院
He's in a convent in Romania.

733
01:11:25,680 --> 01:11:28,670
得了严重的脑热病
He's suffering from a violent brain fever.

734
01:11:29,120 --> 01:11:32,250
修女替他写信
The good sisters are caring for him.They wrote to me,

735
01:11:32,520 --> 01:11:34,580
说他需要我
and they say he needs me...

736
01:11:37,430 --> 01:11:38,590
但....我不去
but I won't go.

737
01:11:39,430 --> 01:11:40,930
我不要丢下你
I'm not going to leave you.

738
01:11:41,000 --> 01:11:42,060
米娜
Mina.

739
01:11:43,470 --> 01:11:45,870
你必须去
You've got to go to him...

740
01:11:46,140 --> 01:11:47,690
你要爱他
and you've got to love him...

741
01:11:48,610 --> 01:11:51,200
立刻嫁给他
and marry him right then and there.

742
01:11:52,810 --> 01:11:55,370
这个你收下
And I want you to take this, my sister.

743
01:11:56,050 --> 01:11:57,910
我送你的贺礼
It's my wedding gift to you.

744
01:11:58,050 --> 01:11:59,520
不,露西
No,Lucy.

745
01:12:00,320 --> 01:12:02,410
别担心任性的小露西
Don't worry about spoiled little Lucy.

746
01:12:04,790 --> 01:12:06,480
我会康复的
I'll be all right.

747
01:12:08,060 --> 01:12:10,360
代我向强纳生致爱
Tell Jonathan oceans of love.

748
01:12:26,010 --> 01:12:27,070
杰克 她怎么了?
Jack, how is she?

749
01:12:46,200 --> 01:12:48,220
我受不了大蒜味
This is why I cannot breathe!

750
01:12:48,300 --> 01:12:49,700
露西 这是药
Lucy, it's medicinal.

751
01:12:49,770 --> 01:12:53,330
会助你睡得好
To help you sleep. To dream better dreams.

752
01:12:53,670 --> 01:12:56,400
只是普通大蒜嘛
It's garlic! It's nothing but common garlic!

753
01:12:56,940 --> 01:12:58,670
昆西来看你了
Quincey's here to see you.

754
01:12:58,840 --> 01:13:00,170
拿点白兰地来
Get some brandy.

755
01:13:00,380 --> 01:13:01,540
露西小姐
Now, Miss Lucy,

756
01:13:01,980 --> 01:13:05,850
你好好休息,阿瑟叫我来看你
you just rest easy.Arthur sent me to take care of you.

757
01:13:06,850 --> 01:13:09,010
他说你不快好,我就得
He said if you don't get better quick...

758
01:13:09,190 --> 01:13:11,590
一枪毙了你,像对跛脚马般
I have to put you out of your misery like a lame horse.

759
01:13:14,590 --> 01:13:17,190
你真野蛮
You're such a beast.

760
01:13:20,200 --> 01:13:22,260
吻我好吗?昆西?
Will you kiss me?Quincey?

761
01:13:25,470 --> 01:13:26,870
吻我
Kiss me.

762
01:13:30,110 --> 01:13:31,100
吻我
Kiss me.

763
01:13:34,740 --> 01:13:36,910
老笨蛋
That old coot!

764
01:13:37,150 --> 01:13:38,740
放开我
Get off me!

765
01:13:39,320 --> 01:13:41,080
露西,听我说
Lucy,Listen to me!

766
01:13:41,320 --> 01:13:43,410
睡觉  快睡觉
Sleep, sleep now. Sleep.

767
01:13:45,860 --> 01:13:47,820
睡吧
You're at peace.

768
01:13:47,820 --> 01:13:48,980
你们看
Look. There. There.

769
01:13:55,570 --> 01:13:56,690
吸血鬼
Nosferatu.

770
01:14:02,170 --> 01:14:04,640
(吸血鬼)

771
01:14:10,780 --> 01:14:13,340
此篇讲述野蛮的
"Here occurs the shocking and frightening history...

772
01:14:14,350 --> 01:14:17,340
德古拉王子骇人野史
of the wild, berserk Prince Dracula...

773
01:14:17,520 --> 01:14:19,510
他将人插住
How he impaled people and roasted them...

774
01:14:19,690 --> 01:14:21,350
烤身、煮头
boiled their heads in a kettle...

775
01:14:21,520 --> 01:14:23,860
活生生的剥皮
how he skinned them alive...

776
01:14:24,030 --> 01:14:27,360
凌迟,饮他们的血
and hacked them to pieces and then drank their blood."

777
01:14:32,270 --> 01:14:33,600
德古拉
Dracul.

778
01:14:34,940 --> 01:14:37,200
血便是生命
For blood is the life.

779
01:14:51,960 --> 01:14:53,890
亲爱的王子
"My dearest Prince,

780
01:14:54,560 --> 01:14:55,890
请原谅我
forgive me.

781
01:14:56,290 --> 01:14:59,560
我收到未婚夫自罗马尼亚的信
I have received word from my fiance in Romania.

782
01:14:59,960 --> 01:15:03,230
我要去见他并完婚
I am en route to join him. We are to be married.

783
01:15:04,500 --> 01:15:06,490
永不再见
I will never see you again.

784
01:15:07,100 --> 01:15:08,430
米娜上
Mina."

785
01:15:18,350 --> 01:15:23,480
奇怪,那位怪友好像也跟来了
It is odd, but I feel almost...that my strange friend is with me.

786
01:15:23,590 --> 01:15:26,110
他在我的思绪中
He speaks to me in my thoughts.

787
01:15:26,260 --> 01:15:29,590
与他在一起我最有活力
With him I felt more alive than ever I had.

788
01:15:30,030 --> 01:15:32,520
如今他不在,又将成婚
And now without him, soon to be a bride...

789
01:15:32,700 --> 01:15:35,190
我深感困惑失落
I feel confused and lost.

790
01:15:35,870 --> 01:15:39,030
也许我虽想做好,其实很坏
Perhaps, though I try to be good, I am bad.

791
01:15:39,870 --> 01:15:42,700
或许我是个善变的坏女人
Perhaps I am a bad, inconstant woman.

792
01:16:01,830 --> 01:16:03,220
飓风！
Winds!

793
01:16:04,230 --> 01:16:05,820
飓风！
Winds!

794
01:16:07,860 --> 01:16:10,990
刮大风吧！
Winds!

795
01:16:14,000 --> 01:16:15,560
就是这原因
It is the cause.

796
01:16:16,240 --> 01:16:18,500
就是它
It is the cause of my soul!

797
01:16:19,180 --> 01:16:20,670
天啊!德古拉
It is Dracula...

798
01:16:21,010 --> 01:16:22,570
这个僵尸
the undead...

799
01:16:22,910 --> 01:16:25,780
我一生追击的敌人
the foe I have pursued all my life.

800
01:16:30,190 --> 01:16:32,120
德古拉!
Dracula!

801
01:16:34,690 --> 01:16:37,350
杰克,快有好多事要告诉你
Jack, hurry! I have much to tell you.

802
01:16:39,600 --> 01:16:41,590
小心守候
Guard her well, Mr. Morris.

803
01:16:41,800 --> 01:16:43,860
今晚不得失误
Do not fail here tonight.

804
01:16:44,030 --> 01:16:49,360
我们对抗的是超越凡人的法力
We are dealing with forces beyond all human experience...an enormous power, so guard her well.

805
01:16:49,710 --> 01:16:53,400
若不尽责你的露西将会成女妖
Otherwise your precious Lucy will become a bitch of the devil...

806
01:16:53,480 --> 01:16:55,270
邪恶的魔女
a whore of darkness!

807
01:16:57,350 --> 01:16:58,870
老疯子
You're a sick old buzzard.

808
01:17:00,550 --> 01:17:02,280
听清楚,小子
Hear me out, young man.

809
01:17:02,450 --> 01:17:05,090
露西不是意外所致
Lucy is not a random victim attacked by mere accident.

810
01:17:05,090 --> 01:17:06,750
明白了吗?   不
Do you understand? No.

811
01:17:06,820 --> 01:17:10,820
她自愿受其蛊惑
She is a willing recruit, a breathless, wanton follower.

812
01:17:10,990 --> 01:17:13,390
忠实的门徒
I dare say, a devoted disciple.

813
01:17:13,560 --> 01:17:16,050
她是魔鬼的姘妇
She is the devil's concubine!

814
01:17:18,000 --> 01:17:19,160
懂了吗
Do you understand me?

815
01:17:20,640 --> 01:17:24,200
但我们仍可救回她的魂
Yet, we may still save her precious soul.

816
01:17:24,510 --> 01:17:28,970
但...得先填饱肚子,杰克
But not on an empty stomach.

817
01:17:29,250 --> 01:17:30,230
杰克  是的,先生
- Jack! - Here, sir.

818
01:17:31,180 --> 01:17:33,510
我饿死了,快跟我去吃
I starve. Feed me.

819
01:17:34,420 --> 01:17:35,710
老傻子！
You old coot!

820
01:19:50,810 --> 01:19:54,140
无能的人类跟愚蠢的驱邪物
Your impotent men with their foolish spells...

821
01:19:54,310 --> 01:19:57,870
保护不了你
cannot protect you from my power.

822
01:20:10,690 --> 01:20:13,490
我诅咒你成为僵尸
I condemn you to living death...

823
01:20:14,260 --> 01:20:16,930
永远
to eternal hunger...

824
01:20:17,600 --> 01:20:21,770
嗜饮...鲜血
for living blood.

825
01:21:46,390 --> 01:21:47,380
杰克
Jack!

826
01:21:55,460 --> 01:21:57,660
我知道你深爱她
I know how deeply you loved her.

827
01:21:57,870 --> 01:21:59,600
所以你得相信
That is why you must trust me and believe.

828
01:21:59,670 --> 01:22:01,660
叫我如何相信?
Believe? How can I believe?

829
01:22:01,940 --> 01:22:05,770
你在天黑前带解剖刀来
I want you to bring me, before nightfall, a set of postmortem knives.

830
01:22:05,940 --> 01:22:07,700
解剖?露西
An autopsy? Lucy?

831
01:22:07,880 --> 01:22:11,540
不算,我要割她的头挖她的心
No, not exactly. I just want to cut off her head and take out her heart.

832
01:22:19,320 --> 01:22:21,950
9月17日,日记
Diary, 17th September.

833
01:22:22,220 --> 01:22:23,820
可怜的强纳生
Poor Jonathan.

834
01:22:24,160 --> 01:22:25,960
他仍重病
He's still so ill.

835
01:22:26,160 --> 01:22:29,060
但回到伦敦他很开心
He's cheered by the familiar streets in London.

836
01:22:29,500 --> 01:22:33,490
而我,因露西已死反而难过
For me, now that Lucy is dead, it is a sad homecoming.

837
01:22:34,840 --> 01:22:37,500
仿佛部份的我也已死去
It is as if a part of me is dead too...

838
01:22:37,640 --> 01:22:40,400
除了暗盼
except for the tiny hope that lives in me...

839
01:22:40,580 --> 01:22:43,070
能再见到我的王子
that I will again see my prince.

840
01:22:43,250 --> 01:22:44,740
他在伦敦吗?
Is he here?

841
01:22:45,850 --> 01:22:46,980
我已结婚,
Now that I am married...

842
01:22:46,980 --> 01:22:51,090
才明白对萦绣山中的他
I begin to understand the nature of my feelings for my strange friend...

843
01:22:51,090 --> 01:22:53,420
是怎样的情绪
who is always in my thoughts.

844
01:23:04,670 --> 01:23:06,600
强纳生,怎么了?
Jonathan, what is it?

845
01:23:06,770 --> 01:23:08,670
就是他
It is the man himself.

846
01:23:09,200 --> 01:23:10,930
他变年轻了
Look, he's grown young.

847
01:23:54,780 --> 01:23:56,110
各位
Gentlemen,

848
01:23:57,250 --> 01:23:59,320
非掘露西的墓不可吗?
must we desecrate poor Lucy's grave?

849
01:23:59,320 --> 01:24:01,260
她死得够惨了
She died horribly enough.

850
01:24:03,960 --> 01:24:07,190
若她已死则无碍
If Miss Lucy is dead, then no wrong can be done to her.

851
01:24:07,400 --> 01:24:08,950
若没死
But if she's not dead...

852
01:24:09,970 --> 01:24:12,200
你是说她被活埋?
What are you saying, man? That she's been buried alive?

853
01:24:12,730 --> 01:24:15,360
不,我只是说
No. All I say is

854
01:24:15,800 --> 01:24:17,290
她没死
she is undead.

855
01:24:18,470 --> 01:24:19,630
没死
Undead.

856
01:24:19,980 --> 01:24:21,530
这真疯狂
This is insane.

857
01:24:40,900 --> 01:24:43,120
各位 动手吧
Gentlemen, shall we?

858
01:24:43,330 --> 01:24:45,730
一、二、三
One, two, three.

859
01:25:03,090 --> 01:25:04,420
她呢?
Where is she?

860
01:25:06,420 --> 01:25:07,910
她呢?
Where is she?

861
01:25:09,260 --> 01:25:10,590
你把她怎么了
What have you done with her?

862
01:25:12,260 --> 01:25:16,930
她住在上帝恩典不及之处飘荡在黑暗界
She lives beyond the grace of God...a wanderer in the outer darkness.

863
01:25:16,930 --> 01:25:19,730
她是吸血鬼
She is vampyre, nosferatu.

864
01:25:20,840 --> 01:25:25,600
这些怪物被吸血后不会死
These creatures do not die like the bee after the first sting...

865
01:25:25,770 --> 01:25:28,770
反受传染而成不朽
but instead grow strong and become immortal...once infected by another nosferatu.

866
01:25:34,280 --> 01:25:35,840
所以,吾友
So my friends,

867
01:25:36,020 --> 01:25:38,280
我们不是对抗一个怪物
we fight not one beast...

868
01:25:38,350 --> 01:25:43,350
而是长久流传以血为生的族群
but legions that go on age after age after age...feeding on the blood of the living.

869
01:25:48,700 --> 01:25:50,960
快躲起来
Quickly, hide. Now.

870
01:26:20,000 --> 01:26:21,460
露西
Lucy!

871
01:26:21,860 --> 01:26:22,590
露西
Lucy!

872
01:26:28,400 --> 01:26:30,500
来,阿瑟
Come to me, Arthur.

873
01:26:31,940 --> 01:26:34,840
扔下其它人,来我这里
Leave these others and come to me.

874
01:26:36,850 --> 01:26:39,780
我好想拥抱你
My arms are hungry for you, my darling.

875
01:26:40,920 --> 01:26:43,580
吻我,抱我
Kiss me and caress me...

876
01:26:43,890 --> 01:26:46,080
我亲爱的丈夫,我求你
my darling husband, please.

877
01:26:46,320 --> 01:26:48,850
我们有十字架和圣水
We wave Christ and His holy blood!

878
01:26:49,160 --> 01:26:51,680
我们在主内坚强
We are strong in the Lord and

879
01:26:51,860 --> 01:26:55,020
主赋与我们力量
the power of His might!

880
01:26:56,260 --> 01:26:59,860
主赋与我们力量
The power of God is upon us!

881
01:27:00,040 --> 01:27:02,700
主赋与我们力量
The power of God is upon us!

882
01:27:04,510 --> 01:27:06,630
主赋与我们力量
The power of God is upon us!

883
01:27:10,310 --> 01:27:12,870
我将你带至光明
I bring you from shadow into light!

884
01:27:13,380 --> 01:27:17,610
黑暗王子,我将你逐至地狱
I cast you out, the prince of darkness...into hell!

885
01:27:20,660 --> 01:27:23,260
只需片刻勇气,
A moment's courage, and it is done.

886
01:27:23,260 --> 01:27:25,190
左手拿凿子
Take the stake in your left hand...

887
01:27:27,130 --> 01:27:29,060
对准心脏
place the point over the heart.

888
01:27:33,900 --> 01:27:36,130
奉主之名,敲下去
Then in God's name, strike. Do it now!

889
01:27:52,020 --> 01:27:53,580
吃呀,大餐
Eat, feast.

890
01:27:54,090 --> 01:27:56,750
将来你们需要力气
You'll need your strength for the dark days ahead.

891
01:27:57,430 --> 01:27:58,420
米娜
Mina?

892
01:27:59,930 --> 01:28:01,090
博士 嗯?
- Doctor? - Ja?

893
01:28:02,830 --> 01:28:04,320
露西怎么死的？
How did Lucy die?

894
01:28:07,700 --> 01:28:08,790
这个...
Well...

895
01:28:10,610 --> 01:28:12,040
她死前痛苦吗？
Was she in great pain?

896
01:28:12,440 --> 01:28:14,770
是的,我们砍掉她的头
Ja, she was in great pain. Then we cut off her head...

897
01:28:15,110 --> 01:28:18,380
在心脏钉下十字架,她就安息了
and drove a stake through her heart and burned it and then she found peace.

898
01:28:18,510 --> 01:28:21,510
博士  拜托别说了
Doctor! Please.

899
01:28:25,450 --> 01:28:26,790
哈克先生
So, Mr. Harker...

900
01:28:27,620 --> 01:28:30,520
身为你的医生,问你个
I must now ask you, as your doctor...

901
01:28:33,400 --> 01:28:34,890
敏感问题
a sensitive question.

902
01:28:35,060 --> 01:28:39,060
你和那些怪物在一起时
During your infidelity with those creatures...those demonic women...

903
01:28:39,200 --> 01:28:41,450
可曾吃过
did you, for one instant,

904
01:28:41,470 --> 01:28:42,800
她们的血
taste of their blood?

905
01:28:44,340 --> 01:28:45,000
没有
No!

906
01:28:49,280 --> 01:28:50,010
没有?
No?

907
01:28:51,210 --> 01:28:52,200
没有
No!

908
01:28:54,650 --> 01:28:55,780
很好
Good!

909
01:28:56,280 --> 01:29:01,120
那你没染上露西那种病
Then you have not infected your blood with the terrible...disease that destroyed poor Lucy.

910
01:29:09,900 --> 01:29:12,160
博士,你要知道
Doctor, you must understand.

911
01:29:13,900 --> 01:29:16,060
以前我疑幻似真
I doubted everything...

912
01:29:16,400 --> 01:29:18,070
甚至以为自己疯了
even my mind.

913
01:29:18,140 --> 01:29:20,300
终日恐惧
I was impotent with fear.

914
01:29:20,810 --> 01:29:21,900
我知道  但是
- I know. - But, sir...

915
01:29:22,080 --> 01:29:26,970
我知道吸血鬼睡在哪
I know where the bastard sleeps.

916
01:29:27,150 --> 01:29:28,810
我把他带到
I brought him there,

917
01:29:29,250 --> 01:29:30,910
卡费教堂
to Carfax Abbey.

918
01:29:33,720 --> 01:29:36,250
吸血鬼的确存在
Vampires do exist.

919
01:29:37,330 --> 01:29:40,320
我们围攻的这一个
And this one we fight, this one we face...

920
01:29:40,600 --> 01:29:43,160
有二十人的力气
has the strength of 20 or more people...

921
01:29:43,330 --> 01:29:45,390
你可以证明
and you can testify for that, Mr. Harker.

922
01:29:46,100 --> 01:29:50,740
他能控制低等的蝙蝠、鼠狼
But he can also control the meaner things of life...the bat, the rodent, the wolf.

923
01:29:50,740 --> 01:29:54,940
可化为烟雾遁形
He can appear as mist, as vapor, as fog and vanish at will.

924
01:29:56,080 --> 01:29:58,010
德古拉法力很大,
Now, all these things Dracula can do...

925
01:29:58,010 --> 01:29:59,680
但他不自由
but he is not free.

926
01:29:59,680 --> 01:30:03,080
他必须躺在故土中增加魔力
He must rest in the sacred earth of his homeland to gain his evil power.

927
01:30:03,250 --> 01:30:06,190
我们必须在此将他毁灭
It is here that we must find him and destroy him utterly.

928
01:30:07,090 --> 01:30:10,350
我替这个伯爵难过
I almost feel pity for anything so hunted as this count.

929
01:30:10,490 --> 01:30:12,480
你怎会怜悯这种怪物
How can you pity such a creature?

930
01:30:14,460 --> 01:30:15,790
我带米娜去我的医院
I'll take Mina to my quarters.

931
01:30:16,200 --> 01:30:17,930
你在那儿才安全
Good. You'll be safer there.

932
01:30:21,500 --> 01:30:24,600
子弹伤不了他,
Mr. Morris, your bullets will not harm him.

933
01:30:24,770 --> 01:30:27,040
一定得砍头 我建议你用猎刀
He must be beheaded. I suggest you use your big bowie knife.

934
01:30:27,210 --> 01:30:30,200
我不打算贴近他,博士
Well, I wasn't plannin' on getting that close, Doc.

935
01:30:31,310 --> 01:30:32,710
主人！
Master!

936
01:30:34,450 --> 01:30:35,880
主人
Master!

937
01:30:37,450 --> 01:30:38,850
主人...
Master!

938
01:30:49,460 --> 01:30:51,230
杰克大夫
Dr. Jack!

939
01:30:52,000 --> 01:30:55,160
我获准得永生
I've been promised eternal life!

940
01:30:57,340 --> 01:30:58,330
杰克
Dr. Seward,

941
01:30:58,410 --> 01:30:59,960
那人是谁
who is that man?

942
01:31:00,140 --> 01:31:02,540
那是伦费先生,你不适合久留
Mr. Renfield. This is no place for you, Madam Mina.

943
01:31:02,740 --> 01:31:06,140
伦费?我得见他
Renfield? I must see him.

944
01:31:06,920 --> 01:31:08,470
伦费先生
Mr. Renfield,

945
01:31:08,920 --> 01:31:10,480
别乱来
behave yourself.

946
01:31:12,820 --> 01:31:14,760
这位是哈克太太
This is Mrs. Harker.

947
01:31:16,490 --> 01:31:17,750
晚安
Good evening.

948
01:31:17,930 --> 01:31:19,830
晚安,伦费先生
Good evening, Mr. Renfield.

949
01:31:20,360 --> 01:31:23,020
我太调皮了
It seems I've been rather naughty.

950
01:31:25,700 --> 01:31:27,030
我认识你
I know you.

951
01:31:27,500 --> 01:31:29,440
你是主人的新娘
You're the bride my master covets.

952
01:31:32,040 --> 01:31:34,270
我有丈夫了
I have a husband.

953
01:31:34,710 --> 01:31:36,370
我是哈克太太
I am Mrs. Harker.

954
01:31:37,710 --> 01:31:40,240
我的主人提过你
My master tells me about you.

955
01:31:41,780 --> 01:31:43,110
他怎么说?
What does he tell you?

956
01:31:44,220 --> 01:31:45,950
说他要来
That he is coming.

957
01:31:47,460 --> 01:31:49,510
他要来找你
That he is coming for you.

958
01:31:49,760 --> 01:31:52,690
过来点
Oh, please.

959
01:31:58,670 --> 01:32:00,690
别留在这
Don't stay here.

960
01:32:01,370 --> 01:32:03,860
离开这些人
Get away from these men,

961
01:32:04,140 --> 01:32:05,470
求求你
please.

962
01:32:07,080 --> 01:32:10,810
我祈求主不要再见到你
And I pray to God I may never see your sweet face again.

963
01:32:14,650 --> 01:32:17,310
愿主祝福保佑你
And may the Lord bless and keep you.

964
01:32:28,760 --> 01:32:30,250
主人！
Master!

965
01:32:30,670 --> 01:32:32,000
主人
Master!

966
01:32:32,430 --> 01:32:35,100
你答应我让我永生的
You promised me eternal life...

967
01:32:35,570 --> 01:32:38,270
你却给了这名美女
but you give it to the pretty woman!

968
01:32:38,770 --> 01:32:40,100
杰克大夫
Dr. Jack!

969
01:32:40,840 --> 01:32:42,830
我不是疯子
I'm no lunatic man!

970
01:32:43,010 --> 01:32:45,910
我很正常,在为灵魂奋战
I'm a sane man fighting for his soul!

971
01:32:46,110 --> 01:32:49,450
我的房间很简陋,但很舒适
My quarters are spare, but I think you will find them comfortable.

972
01:32:50,450 --> 01:32:52,010
杰克大夫
Dr. Jack!

973
01:32:52,290 --> 01:32:54,850
有水和清洁用品
Water and toiletries at your disposal.

974
01:32:57,430 --> 01:32:59,590
你在这十分安全
You'll be completely safe here.

975
01:34:01,820 --> 01:34:03,480
毁掉每个箱子
Destroy every box.

976
01:34:03,660 --> 01:34:05,720
浇圣水
Sterilize the earth inside.

977
01:34:05,930 --> 01:34:07,420
让他无处可逃
Leave him no refuge.

978
01:34:08,000 --> 01:34:09,990
开始驱魔
Let the exorcism begin.

979
01:34:36,790 --> 01:34:38,120
伦费
Renfield.

980
01:34:39,560 --> 01:34:42,220
你背叛了我
You have betrayed me.

981
01:34:43,830 --> 01:34:45,060
没有
No.

982
01:34:46,630 --> 01:34:48,530
主人,我没有
